wings of life ( known as &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; in france and hidden beauty : a love story that feeds the earth in the united kingdom ) is a 2011 french-american nature documentary film directed by louis &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and released by disneynature . it was released theatrically in france on march 16 , 2011 , with narration by melanie laurent , and in home media markets across the us on april 16 , 2013 , with narration by meryl streep .